metadata.name: BIRTH
metadata.description:
BIRTH - To be born means beating the odds, to live means more odds to beat.

In certain ways, art can be used as a tool to share and express experiences that can be relatable to us. “The Experience” is a black and white series of images that observes relatable stages that everyone has or will come into contact with on some level throughout our most common experience of all, the human experience.
